        {
            "title": "西九龍走廊往葵涌方向4車相撞 至少1人受傷 近興華街全線封閉",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/0a4eb12ce7ea6e8b80133a6e3d4ed0f7/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250206/_2025020617213156717.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\"></figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>西九龍走廊發生交通意外。今日（6日）下午4時許，4輛私家車於西九龍走廊往美孚方向行駛，至宇晴軒附近時發生相撞，涉及3輛私家車及1輛的士。消息指，一名司機報稱頸部受傷，救援人員正趕往現場施救。\n\n</p>\n<p>運輸署表示，現時上址交通繁忙，西九龍走廊(往葵涌方向)近興華街的全線現已封閉，呼籲駕駛人士改用其他道路。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4063395/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/5f22bb151068727346481a4818e53220/2025-02/d27078eb-ea52-4cf3-8015-fd876c140cd9.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2051220/即時-港聞-西九龍走廊往葵涌方向4車相撞-至少1人受傷-近興華街全線封閉",
            "pub_date": "2025-02-06 17:25:53",
